      "- Can now roll [Primal Hunger](Primal_Hunger.md \"Primal Hunger\"), [Scarred Faith](Scarred_Faith.md \"Scarred Faith\"), and [Wildsurge Incantation](Wildsurge_Incantation.md \"Wildsurge Incantation\").\\[Undocumented]",
